data.description: This twin home nestled in the historic district of Reading boasts Victorian charm and ample space. With five bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms, it offers generous accommodation for a family or those who enjoy entertaining guests. Situated near Centre Park, residents have convenient access to local shopping and dining options, making it an ideal blend of historic charm and modern convenience.
